structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.catch_line: Powers conferred by KRS 99.520 to 99.590 supplemental.
law.text: The powers conferred by KRS 99.520 to 99.590 shall be in addition and supplemental to the powers conferred by any other law.
law.history: Created 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 215, sec. 8, effective February 28, 1956.
